data.description: Tired of looking at cookie cutter builder floor plans? This home offering a unique and captivating floor plan. This spacious residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms. Step inside and be greeted by an inviting foyer that leads you into the heart of the home. The open-concept layout of the dining and kitchen areas. The kitchen is a true chef's delight that makes meal preparation a breeze. The ample cabinetry offers plenty of storage options for all your culinary needs. The home also includes a spacious bonus room that can serve as a guest room, home office, or playroom. Adjacent to the bedroom is a stylishly appointed bathroom, offering convenience and privacy for guests or family members. The backyard has multiple raised garden beds to grow your own food! Not to mention the shed with electricty! The location of this home offers a desirable combination of suburban tranquility and convenient access to amenities. Enjoy easy access to schools, parks, shopping centers, and dining options, ensuring that all your needs are met within a short distance.
